snippet: Baltimore tied for first in the American League East with a blowout of Toronto. The Orioles last shared first in September in 1997.
abstract: MLB Roundup; Baltimore Orioles defeat Toronto Blue Jays, 12-0, to move into a first-place tie in the American League East; other results noted.
lead_paragraph: Baltimore tied for first in the American League East with a blowout of Toronto. The Orioles last shared first in September in 1997.

headline.seo: Orioles Beat Blue Jays and Tie Yankees for First in A.L. East
headline.main: Orioles Surge to Share of East Lead
headline.print_headline: Orioles Surge To Share Of East Lead
